  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Building Bridges to Peace</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The USAID/CMM-funded Building Bridges to Peace (BBP) program sought to address the key causes of conflict in and around northern Karamoja by engaging communities in inter-group dialogues and joint livelihoods projects that build mutual interest and promote reconciliation. Its main objectives were to strengthen local mechanisms for conflict mitigation, support reconciliation through dialogues and trust-building measures, and build cooperation and address key causes of violence through joint livelihoods projects.</narrative>
  </description>
